# LICENSE-NOTICE — internal/ptyhost/

This directory contains code lifted from the OpenOva platform, specifically the
Sandbox pty-server runtime. The lift was performed at a stable handoff point
agreed between the chepherd and openova teams.

## Source

- Repository: https://github.com/openova-io/openova
- Tag:        pty-server-handoff-1.0
- Commit:     c65dbdca
- Path:       products/sandbox/pty-server/internal/{session,server,agentcatalog}

## Scope of the lift

- session/session.go, buffer.go, manager.go     — PTY multiplexer + ring buffer
- server/routes.go, metrics.go                  — HTTP/WS surface for client attach
- agentcatalog/agentcatalog.go                  — agent CLI registry (claude-code,
                                                   qwen-code, aider, cursor-agent,
                                                   little-coder, opencode,
                                                   sovereign-shell)

## Modifications applied during the lift

1. Import paths rewritten: `github.com/openova-io/openova/products/sandbox/pty-server/internal/*`
   → `github.com/chepherd/chepherd/internal/ptyhost/*`
2. Environment variable rename: `OPENOVA_SANDBOX_AGENTS_PATH` → `CHEPHERD_AGENTS_PATH`
3. No other modifications. The runtime semantics, wire protocol, ring buffer
   behavior, and agent-spawn contract are bit-identical to the openova source
   at the tagged commit.

