## Coordination

This lift was agreed via chepherd/chepherd EPIC #49 and openova-io/openova
issue #2316. Both teams committed to keeping the wire protocol stable so
future bug-fixes can be cross-applied. chepherd's MCP server uses the
`chepherd.*` namespace; openova-MCP keeps `gitea.*`, `sandbox.db.*`,
`k8s.*`, `marketplace.*`, `sandbox.deploy.*`, `sandbox.stripe.*` —
non-colliding by agreement.

